metadata.name: Fame Lady #1
metadata.description: Fame Lady Squad is the first ever generative all-female avatar collection on the Ethereum blockchain. Yes, we are THE community who took over a project to write our own story. This is NFT history. This is HERstory. FLS are 8888 distinctive Ladies made up of millions of fierce trait combinations. Community = Everything. Commercial IP rights of each Lady NFT belong to its owner.
